Subject: Doctor Who (season 9) 
To: Dick
Content:
The 9th season of British science fiction television series Doctor Who began on 1 January 1972 with Day of the Daleks, and ended with The Time Monster. Jon Pertwee continues his role as the Third Doctor, as does Katy Manning playing Jo Grant. Roger Delgado returns to play The Master in The Sea Devils and The Time Monster. Nicholas Courtney, John Levene and Richard Franklin continue their roles of Brigadier Lethbridge-Stewart, Sergeant Benton and Captain Mike Yates respectfully. All serials of season 9 have been released on DVD all individually and some in multi-serial box sets.
I read the paragraph on http://wikipedia.org
